{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.640", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.520", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.600", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.040", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die AfD will die deutsche Sprache im Grundgesetz verankern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.520", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.400", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "CSU und CDU sowie der ehemalige Bundestagspr\u00e4sident Norbert Lammert vertreten dies bereits seit langem."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.040", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Bundestag gab es dazu Anh\u00f6rungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.040", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Stellungnahmen und Petitionen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.040", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bisher aber keine Mehrheit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.680", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist bedauerlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.240", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber sicher keine Katastrophe."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.160", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Rechtswissenschaft schreibt heute schon der deutschen Sprache ihren Verfassungsrang zu. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.200", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ergibt sich aus unserer Verfassung: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.200", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "durch die Nennung des deutschen Volkes, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.360", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der deutschen Staatsangeh\u00f6rigkeit und durch die Tatsache, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.920", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass unser Grundgesetz auf Deutsch geschrieben wurde. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.800", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Au\u00dferdem ist Deutsch unter anderem im Gerichtsverfassungsgesetz und im Verwaltungsverfahrensgesetz verankert."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.600", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es w\u00e4re aber auch aus unserer Sicht ein wichtiges Signal, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.200", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die deutsche Sprache symbolisch im Grundgesetz explizit aufzuf\u00fchren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.520", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sorgt f\u00fcr gesellschaftlichen Zusammenhalt und Identit\u00e4t. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.600", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt viele Verfassungen in Europa, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.920", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die die Landessprache normiert haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.640", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen ist die Forderung per se auch nichts Schlechtes oder gar Schlimmes."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.240", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deutsch zu sprechen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.640", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist Voraussetzung f\u00fcr Teilhabe in Deutschland."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.880", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir f\u00f6rdern deshalb Sprachkitas, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.840", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "berufsbezogene sprachliche F\u00f6rderprogramme, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.000", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Integrationskurse und vieles mehr. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.680", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.400", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit dem Bayerischen Integrationsgesetz verpflichten wir auch zur Teilnahme an Sprachkursen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.040", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn wir wollen keine Parallelgesellschaften in Deutschland."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.920", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Solche Ma\u00dfnahmen sind f\u00fcr den Schutz der deutschen Sprache in der Praxis grunds\u00e4tzlich viel wichtiger als reine Symbolpolitik."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.200", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen von der AfD, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.480", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihr Gesetzentwurf ist wie \u00fcblich oberfl\u00e4chlich formuliert und bei der L\u00f6sung inhaltslos."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.000", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie wollen die deutsche Sprache nicht als Symbol verankert wissen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.640", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern als Staatsziel, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.600", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Sie wollen damit quasi Sprachpolizei spielen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.000", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie stehen im krassen Widerspruch zu den meisten Rechtskommentaren und dem Wissenschaftlichen Dienst des Bundestages."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.560", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich darf aus Ihrem Gesetzentwurf zitieren:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.520", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "...\u00a0Unternehmen nutzen die englische Sprache bevorzugt nicht nur f\u00fcr ihre unternehmensinterne Kommunikation, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.680", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern ebenso f\u00fcr Werbema\u00dfnahmen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.320", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wollen Sie Unternehmen also allen Ernstes vorschreiben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.480", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie sie ihre Werbung gestalten sollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.120", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "oder gar, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.600", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie sie intern kommunizieren?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.320", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie schreiben weiter:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.520", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deutschsprachige Musiker sehen sich zunehmend gezwungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.040", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auf Englisch zu singen\u00a0..."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.600", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wollen Sie unseren Radio- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.800", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Fernsehsendern vorschreiben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.440", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "welche Musik sie spielen m\u00fcssen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.160", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "oder uns gar, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.560", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "welche Musik wir h\u00f6ren d\u00fcrfen?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.960", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie wollen in Ihrem Gesetzentwurf f\u00fcr die \u00f6ffentliche Kommunikation staatlicher Institutionen \u00fcber die bereits verankerte Festlegung der deutschen Sprache hinaus weitere Vorgaben machen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.800", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wollen Sie vielleicht bei wissenschaftlichen Kongressen in Deutschland den Wissenschaftlern aus aller Welt vorschreiben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.720", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie nur deutsch zu sprechen haben?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.120", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich muss Ihnen ehrlich sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.520", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich bin stolz auf die vielen jungen Leute in unserem Land, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.800", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die in der Lage sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.640", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sich auf Englisch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.760", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Franz\u00f6sisch und Spanisch zu verst\u00e4ndigen"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.600", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und auch einen ganzen Artikel in den Sprachen zu verfassen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.360", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In der Arbeitswelt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.360", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in der Wissenschaft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.400", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in der Forschung ist die Vielsprachigkeit schlicht gar nicht mehr wegzudenken."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.920", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zu guter Letzt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.560", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Besonders entt\u00e4uschend ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "239.880", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Ihr Gesetzentwurf mehr als scheinheilig ist\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "239.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.680", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "samt den Schaufensterreden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.040", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Sie hier gehalten haben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.160", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Kollegin Lindholz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.720", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gestatten Sie eine Zwischenfrage?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.520", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nein."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.240", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.160", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie gestatten keine Zwischenfrage."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "257.640", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nicht nur Ihr Programm ist auf Russisch ver\u00f6ffentlicht worden; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "257.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.440", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Kollegin Connemann hat bereits darauf hingewiesen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "267.600", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben im Bundestagswahlkampf und in den Landtagswahlk\u00e4mpfen in Nordrhein-Westfalen und in Berlin auch mit Flyern"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "267.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.560", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und auf Wahlplakaten auf Russisch geworben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "270.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "277.600", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer sich hier als Polizei und gro\u00dfer Verteidiger der deutschen Sprache aufspielt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "277.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "280.400", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der muss das erst einmal erkl\u00e4ren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "280.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "282.800", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was Sie hier abliefern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "282.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "288.520", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist an Scheinheiligkeit wirklich nicht mehr zu \u00fcberbieten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "288.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "290.160", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihnen geht es nicht darum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "290.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "294.640", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die deutsche Sprache als eine sch\u00f6ne Sprache im Grundgesetz zu verankern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "294.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "296.040", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihnen geht es wie \u00fcblich darum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "296.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "296.800", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu spalten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "296.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "299.120", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich m\u00f6chte mit Goethe schlie\u00dfen:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "299.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "299.560", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein jeder, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "299.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "300.280", 
   "id": "s000090", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil er spricht, "
   ]
  }, 
